# Comparing the Four States of Data

| Property          | Raw       | Structured | Semi-Structured | Unstructured |
| ----------------- | --------- | ---------- | --------------- | ------------ |
| Organized         | No        | Yes        | Partial         | No           |
| Easy to Analyze   | Difficult | Easy       | Moderate        | Difficult    |
| Human Readability | High      | High       | High            | Varies       |
| Machine Friendly  | Low       | High       | Moderate        | Low          |
| Examples          | Logs      | SQL Tables | JSON            | Images       |

